2011-12-11 08:24  peroyvind

	* NEWS, configure.ac, find-requires.in: "resolve" /bin/env foo
	  interpreter to actual path, rather than generating
	  dependencies on coreutils, should trim off ~800 dependencies more

2011-12-11 06:57  peroyvind

	* NEWS, find-requires.in: drop automatically generated dependencies
	  on interpreters we either don't
	  need dependencies on or that we have other dedicated dependency
	  generators
	  for making them duplicate, reducing another ~5K packages'
	  dependencies at
	  next rebuild.

2011-12-11 06:24  peroyvind

	* NEWS, configure.ac, find-requires.in: drop automatically
	  generated rtld(GNU_HASH) dependencies, it's been provided
	  by glibc for five years now and can safely be assumed that
	  there's no longer
	  any need for it, reducing ~5K packages' dependency on it during
	  next rebuild.

